## Design System (CRITICAL)

**Always use design tokens from `tailwind.config.ts`:**

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Use palette tokens
className="bg-palette-forest-dark text-white"
className="border-palette-olive hover:bg-palette-sage"

// ❌ BAD - Hardcoded colors
className="bg-[#2c3e2e] text-white"
```

**Color palette:**
- `palette-forest-dark`, `palette-forest-darker` - Primary actions
- `palette-olive`, `palette-sage` - Secondary, backgrounds
- `palette-gold`, `palette-amber` - Highlights
- `palette-strava` - Strava integration
- `palette-danger` - Errors, destructive actions

**Component library:**
- Use existing components: `Button`, `Input`, `SearchInput`, `Dropdown`, `Textarea`, `Badge`, `Modal`, `DashboardPageShell`
- Use existing icons: `IconClose`, `IconRunning`, `IconBiking`, etc. from `components/SportIcons.tsx`
- Check `docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` before creating new components
- **When adding a new reusable component:** document it in `docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` (Composants section: name, usage, code example), update the table of contents and the "Fichiers clés" list at the end

**Tuiles entraînement / calendrier (règles strictes):**
- **Couleur des tuiles = sport uniquement.** Bordure et badge des tuiles d'entraînement viennent toujours de `lib/sportStyles.ts` → `SPORT_CARD_STYLES` (course = forest-dark, vélo = olive, natation = sky, musculation = stone, etc.). Ne jamais utiliser une autre logique (ex. moment de la journée, statut) pour la couleur.
- **Icônes sport = `components/SportIcons.tsx` uniquement.** Utiliser `IconRunning`, `IconBiking`, `IconSwimming`, `IconDumbbell`, etc. (via `SPORT_ICONS`). **Pas d'emojis** (🏃, 🚴, etc.) pour les sports.

**Centralized utilities:**
- Date operations → `lib/dateUtils.ts`
- String operations → `lib/stringUtils.ts`
- Auth checks → `lib/authHelpers.ts`
- Form validation → `lib/workoutValidation.ts`
- Form styles → `lib/formStyles.ts`
- Sport styles → `lib/sportStyles.ts`
- Error handling → `lib/errors.ts`
- Logging → `lib/logger.ts`

