## Component Patterns

### Dashboard Pages
**Always use `DashboardPageShell`** instead of raw `<main>` tags (pas de titre en tête de page ; le shell fournit uniquement la card et la zone scrollable) :

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD
import { DashboardPageShell } from '@/components/DashboardPageShell'

export default function MyPage() {
  return (
    <DashboardPageShell>
      {/* contenu */}
    </DashboardPageShell>
  )
}

// ❌ BAD - Don't duplicate layout
export default function MyPage() {
  return (
    <main className="flex-1 flex flex-col h-full...">
      <div className="flex-1 overflow-y-auto...">
        {/* contenu */}
      </div>
    </main>
  )
}
```

### Modals
**Always use the centralized `<Modal>` component:**

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD
import { Modal } from '@/components/Modal'

<Modal isOpen={isOpen} onClose={onClose} title="Titre" size="md">
  {/* contenu */}
</Modal>

// ❌ BAD - Don't create custom portals
import { createPortal } from 'react-dom'
createPortal(<div>...</div>, document.body)
```

### Forms
**Use centralized form styles:**

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Import from lib
import { FORM_BASE_CLASSES, FORM_ERROR_CLASSES } from '@/lib/formStyles'

// ❌ BAD - Redefine locally
const BASE_CLASSES = 'w-full px-4 py-3...'
```

### Sport Styles
**Use centralized sport styles:**

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Import from lib
import { SPORT_LABELS, SPORT_ICONS, SPORT_CARD_STYLES } from '@/lib/sportStyles'

// ❌ BAD - Redefine locally
const SPORT_LABELS = { course: 'Course', ... }
```

