## User Roles

| Role | Can | Cannot |
|------|-----|--------|
| **Athlete** | View workouts, send requests (with offer choice), chat, rate coach | Create workouts for others |
| **Coach** | Create offers (draft → published → archived), accept/decline requests, manage athletes, create workouts | Access other coaches' data |
| **Admin** | Manage members, view all data | Break RLS policies |

